{
  "stem": "13981.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But we also went, on that same trip, to a little place called Mittenwald, which is famous for the violins that are being built there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it so happened that, during the war, we took that place, our regiment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the one who interrupted the negotiation, the surrender negotiations, for that little place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the exception of Franz Papen I think I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] rest of them-- Fritzsche I'm sure should not have been blamed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He shouldn't even have been in the trial, because he was a newcomer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had only been in the job six weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it's well-known that Goebbels was the former minister of propaganda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he realized that the situation became untenable, he shot his wife and seven children and then shot himself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Fritzsche was the one who took Goebbels' place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't think he had anything to do with the-- and he was acquitted, and I felt that was correct.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I figured they were getting old enough, where they were harmless, really harmless, at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just, for instance, I was against Hess being held in Spandau, where we had to have the pretty near military establishment just for him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought it useless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not that his sentence wasn't appropriate, but I felt, at that time, it was a useless undertaking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lumber.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went right back into the lumber business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1949, I had a chance to go to Mexico.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had an offer down there that paid me twice as much as I was actually receiving here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while in Mexico, I met my now wife, Alicia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moreno.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
